Cell.Data: Text surrounded by {} or [] are special tags for code. These tag will be replaced with other text eg: the name of a player. The tags should NOT be localized. They represent the place in the sentens for their replacing string. Some {} tags start with STR or INT. STR means it will be replaced with text, INT means it will be replaced with a numerical value

All the text in this XML are names of sectors. Sector names are displayed in the game above the corresponding sectors on the strategic map.
Some names differ from their text ID, DO NOT MODIFY THE TEXT ID! The modified name is correct and is the one should be translated
